                            <comment id="17270992" author="dongjoon" created="Sun, 24 Jan 2021 21:42:40 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Thank you for reporting, &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=jack86596&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;jack86596&quot;&gt;jack86596&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="17271069" author="dongjoon" created="Mon, 25 Jan 2021 05:18:48 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I confirmed that this exists in Apache Spark 3.1.1 RC1, too.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;
spark-sql&amp;gt; select * from test_decimal;
10.000
Time taken: 3.436 seconds, Fetched 1 row(s)

spark-sql&amp;gt; select version();
3.1.1 53fe365edb948d0e05a5ccb62f349cd9fcb4bb5d
Time taken: 0.158 seconds, Fetched 1 row(s)
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="17271071" author="dongjoon" created="Mon, 25 Jan 2021 05:21:57 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;As a workaround, you may want to turn off `spark.sql.hive.convertMetastoreParquet`.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;
spark-sql&amp;gt; set spark.sql.hive.convertMetastoreParquet=&lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;false&lt;/span&gt;;
spark.sql.hive.convertMetastoreParquet	&lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;false&lt;/span&gt;
Time taken: 0.04 seconds, Fetched 1 row(s)

spark-sql&amp;gt; select * from test_decimal;
100.000
Time taken: 1.695 seconds, Fetched 1 row(s)
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="17271075" author="dongjoon" created="Mon, 25 Jan 2021 05:41:37 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Also, this happens only in Parquet. For ORC, it works correctly.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;
spark-sql&amp;gt; select * from orc_decimal;
100.000
Time taken: 1.631 seconds, Fetched 1 row(s) &lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="17271098" author="dongjoon" created="Mon, 25 Jan 2021 07:16:04 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;It seems that I found the root cause. I&apos;ll make a PR soon.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
